Description: CVE-2025-15079 - libssh knownhosts global file bypass
 When doing SSH-based transfers using either SCP or SFTP with libssh,
 and setting the known_hosts file, libcurl could still mistakenly accept
 connecting to hosts not present in the specified file if they were added
 as recognized in the libssh global known_hosts file. This patch sets
 both SSH_OPTIONS_KNOWNHOSTS and SSH_OPTIONS_GLOBAL_KNOWNHOSTS to the
 same user-specified file, preventing fallback to the global file.
